The first inauguration of Bill Clinton as the 42nd President of the United States was held on January 20 , 1993 on the West Front of the United States Capitol Building in Washington , D.C. .
The inauguration marked the commencement of the first four-year term of Bill Clinton as President and Al Gore as Vice President .
At of age time of his first inauguration , Clinton was the third-youngest person to become president , and the first from the Baby Boomer generation .